auth.basic.generated_token1:
1. MyAppページを開きます (先にログインしておく必要があります):

https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps

2. "Create App"をクリックして進みます
3. "{{.API}}"を選択
4. "{{.TypeOfAccess}}"を選択
5. アプリケーション名をつけて入力してください
6. "Create App"をクリックして進みます
7. "Generated access token"欄の近くにある"Generate"ボタンを押します
8. 生成されたトークン文字列をコピーします

doc.readme.title: Tools for Dropbox and Dropbox Business.
doc.readme.body.license:
watermint toolbox is licensed under the MIT license.
Please see LICENSE.md or LICENSE.txt for more detail.
doc.readme.body.usage:
`tbx` have various features. Run without an option for a list of supported commands and options.
You can see available commands and options by running executable without arguments like below.
domain.model.mo_activity.event.event_cat: Filter the returned events to a single category
domain.model.mo_activity.event.event_typ: The particular type of action taken
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.abb: An abbreviated form of the person's name.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.bro: Information on the browser used for this web session.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.cli: The Dropbox desktop client type (windows, mac, or linux)
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.cou: The country from which the last activity from this session was made.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.cre: The time this session was created.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.dev: Type of the session (web_session, desktop_client, or mobile_client)
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.dis: A name that can be used directly to represent the name of a user's Dropbox account.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.ext: External ID that a team can attach to the user.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.giv: Also known as a first name
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.ip_: The IP address of the last activity from this session.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.is_: Whether it's possible to delete all of the account files upon unlinking.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.las: Last carrier used by the device.
Information on the hosting operating system
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.sta: The user's status as a member of a specific team. (active/invited/suspended/removed)
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.sur: Also known as a last name or family name.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.tea: ID of user as a member of a team.
domain.model.mo_device.membersession.upd: The time of the last activity from this session.
domain.model.mo_file_diff.diff.diff_type: Type of difference. `file_content_diff`: different content hash, `{left|right}_file_missing`: left or right file missing, `{left|right}_folder_missing`: left or right folder missing.
Number of files and folders under the folder
Number of files under the folder
Number of folders under the folder
